Rion:

Rion flapped his wings and kicked up a semi-large dust cloud in his attempt 
at flight. Okay, so he had never really been one for running, even though he 
was good at it. Diana was the real athletic one. She was always challenging 
him to some sort of race or contest:

Rion coughed a couple of times before he finally got airborne. He flapped 
twice, and managed to stay a couple feet off the ground before nearly 
crashing into it. He skimmed along the surface for awhile, flapping 
occasionally. He wasn't ging too fast, about the average fast walking speed, 
but at least he wasn't walking anymore!

"C'mon! If we can find some trees or something we might find other 'bots 
too!"
